00:08:55.669 --> 00:08:56.871
- You want this for a
bit?

112
00:08:56.904 --> 00:08:58.439
- Captain. I'm okay.

113
00:08:58.472 --> 00:08:59.573
- Are you sure?

114
00:08:59.607 --> 00:09:01.142
- Yeah. thank you.

115
00:09:02.009 --> 00:09:02.877
- Okay.

116
00:09:11.018 --> 00:09:12.620
