212
00:14:42.550 --> 00:14:46.253
Hearing like a nice swanky chic
oasis.

213
00:14:47.121 --> 00:14:48.288
And I didn't get an invite.

214
00:14:51.291 --> 00:14:52.159
Sam.

215
