a while to go away.

246
00:16:25.452 --> 00:16:28.288
But next time around.
this'll all feel normal.

247
00:16:28.322 --> 00:16:30.057
It's just 'cause it's your first
time.

248
00:16:32.292 --> 00:16:33.427
All right. you rest up.

249
00:16:33.460 --> 00:16:35.496
